==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unbusied
<hw>Un*bus"ied</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not required to
work; unemployed; not busy.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>These <qex>unbusied</qex> persons can continue in this playing
idleness till it become a toil.</q> <rj><qau>Bp. Rainbow</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unbutton</ent>⟦br⟧
